{"tid":1899842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全港工會人員唔該入一入黎","createTime":"2020-02-27T00:46:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T00:56:37.000Z","uid":42108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"381498470ac32886a921e5346f8c953c455b1ce3","tid":1899842,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T00:46:13.000Z","msg":"依家已經醫護開始比人清算<br />\n<br />\n唔係淨係想旨意佢地醫護<br />\n<br />\n不過佢地已經打爛左個碗<br />\n<br />\n你地想比佢地製造嘅白色恐怖控制著<br />\n<br />\n定搞多次罷工反抗 <br />\n<br />\n唔該真係要快少少做 拖越耐醫護個邊就越大壓力<br />\n<br />\n至於醫護個邊<br />\n<br />\n骨氣食唔到飯 但係依家佢地好明顯就係殺雞儆猴<br />\n<br />\n你地想有骨氣咁罷多次工/集體請辭<br />\n<br />\n定要日夜擔心個飯碗同埋條命入dirty team 輪shift？"},{"pid":"c294ee251e6370afdba73879060307438ec53889","tid":1899842,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T00:46:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f27e04b888e09897ea1c7d81b0ec33826d6b95a","tid":1899842,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T00:46:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2238d7eb0b06bc21e2e3cd9542b945fade2282a4","tid":1899842,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T00:47:33.000Z","msg":"工會真係要肯踏出第一步呼籲"},{"pid":"30833e5da9d7dbeded5353af7a044f165d2bc5bc","tid":1899842,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T00:47:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37aebeb7d743dd19b2caefd377c816ce1ae06c77","tid":1899842,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T00:47:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"010bc617810cf1e7648648c5a673aaf52cbb2be9","tid":1899842,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T00:49:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同埋參與嘅罷工人士真係要知道咩叫罷工<br />\n唔係一日半日就算 係要長期<br />\n如果驚就唔好做無人會怪你<br />\n不過諗吓要因為飯碗而擔憂<br />\n定再嘗試反抗</span></span>"},{"pid":"ffad95c4377d30c9e98331a18711ae0925bd9b61","tid":1899842,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020